              "label": "(a)",
              "token": "a",
              "kind": "alpha_lower",
              "text": "A process to be used to establish criteria, make decisions and adopt a land use final order related to the light rail route and other project improvements to be included in the Southwest Corridor MAX Light Rail Project, including their locations;",
