ts and maintenance facilities means the light rail stations, light rail park-and-ride lots and light rail vehicle maintenance facilities to be selected from among alternatives described in a Draft Statement, Final Statement or similar document to be included in the project. (17) TriMet means the Tri-County Metropolitan Transportation District of Oregon, a mass transit district created under ORS chapter 267. [2017 c.714 1] Note:",
